00:01:14.080 --> 00:01:15.820
AUDIENCE: Well as
we did last lecture,

00:01:15.820 --> 00:01:23.580
we crossed off the k2
because that's the slow step.

00:01:23.580 --> 00:01:26.201
So it doesn't matter as much.

00:01:26.201 --> 00:01:27.200
CATHERINE DRENNAN: Yeah.

00:01:27.200 --> 00:01:30.770
And so when you get rid of
