temperature effect

00:39:03.330 --> 00:39:06.360
with equilibrium constants?

00:39:06.360 --> 00:39:07.760
Yes.

00:39:07.760 --> 00:39:09.480
The van 't Hoff equation.

00:39:09.480 --> 00:39:11.820
I told you that some
